      "name": "Wall shear stress distribution — qualitative variability assessment",
      "description": "Wall shear stress distributions on impeller blades compared against PIV-derived estimates. Inherent variability in blade surface finish and rotational speed fluctuation was assessed qualitatively by engineering judgment; no structured probability distribution or Monte Carlo sweep was performed for this result. Spatial agreement rated acceptable at mid-range operating point; off-design scatter noted but attributed to experimental setup variability without formal characterisation."
